title: BRIEF-Paycom Software Reports Q1 Non-GAAP Earnings Per Share $0.95
text:
May 1 (Reuters) - Paycom Software Inc:
* PAYCOM SOFTWARE, INC. REPORTS FIRST QUARTER 2018 RESULTS * Q1 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.95
* Q1 GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.70 * Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.90 — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* SEES Q2 2018 REVENUE $123 MILLION TO $125 MILLION * Q1 REVENUE $153.9 MILLION VERSUS I/B/E/S VIEW $151.2 MILLION
* SEES FY TOTAL REVENUE IN RANGE OF $545.0 MILLION TO $547.0 MILLION
* Q2 REVENUE VIEW $123.8 MILLION — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S * FY2018 REVENUE VIEW $544.0 MILLION — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
